        scenarioTitle: 'A canary appears healthy but misses the risk',
        scenarioContext: 'The canary includes internal users with small files, while the first enterprise client has far larger volume and a different payer mapping.',
        decision: 'How should the rollout design change?',
        recommendation: 'Select canary segments that represent volume, configuration, and integration risk; use synthetic load where real exposure is unsafe; define business and technical thresholds; and include adequate bake time before expansion.',
